<lb n="1118a06" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1118a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118a08" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="1118002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（西晉…譯））十一字＝（（竺法護譯））四字【宋】【宮】，（（西晉三藏法師竺法護譯））十字【元】【明】，〔西晉…譯〕－【聖】</note><app word-count="11" n="1118002"><lem>西晉月氏國三藏竺法護譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">西晉三藏法師竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a0901">聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。與
<lb n="1118a10" ed="T"/>大比丘眾俱。比丘五百及諸菩薩。</p>
<lb n="1118a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a1101">爾時世尊告諸比丘。將來之世當有比丘。因
<lb n="1118a12" ed="T"/>有一法不從法化。令法毀滅不得長益。何謂
<lb n="1118a13" ed="T"/>為一。不護禁戒。不能守心。不修智慧。放逸其
<lb n="1118a14" ed="T"/>意。唯求<note n="1118003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善＝華【宮】</note><app n="1118003"><lem>善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">華</rdg></app>名不順道教。不肯<note n="1118004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勤＝謹【宋】【元】</note><app n="1118004"><lem>勤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">謹</rdg></app>慕度世之
<lb n="1118a15" ed="T"/>業。是為一事。令法毀滅。</p>
<lb n="1118a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a1601">佛告比丘。復有二事令法毀滅。何謂為二。一
<lb n="1118a17" ed="T"/>不護禁戒。不攝其心不修智慧。畜妻養子放
<lb n="1118a18" ed="T"/>心恣意。賈作治<note n="1118005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝產【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118005"><lem>生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">產</rdg></app>。以<note n="1118006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">共相＝相供【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">共相＝相供【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118006"><lem>共相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">相供</rdg></app>活。二伴黨相著。
<lb n="1118a19" ed="T"/>憎奉法者欲令<note n="1118007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陷＝墜【宮】</note><app n="1118007"><lem>陷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">墜</rdg></app>墮。故為言<note n="1118008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">義＝儀【三】，議【宮】</note><note n="1118008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義＝儀【宋】【元】【明】，＝議【宮】</note><app n="1118008"><lem>義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">儀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">議</rdg></app>謂之<note n="1118009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諛＝諭【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1118009"><lem>諛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">諭</rdg></app>諂。
<lb n="1118a20" ed="T"/><note n="1118010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">內＋（私）【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內＋（私）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118010"><lem>內</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">內私</rdg></app>犯惡<note n="1118011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118011"><lem>行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。外<note n="1118012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佯＝揚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佯＝揚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118012"><lem>佯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">揚</rdg></app>清白。是為二事。令法毀
<lb n="1118a21" ed="T"/>滅。</p>
<lb n="1118a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a2201">佛告<note n="1118013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1118013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1118013"><lem>諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘。復有三事。令法毀滅。何謂為
<lb n="1118a23" ed="T"/>三。一既不護<note n="1118014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔禁〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔禁〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118014"><lem>禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1118015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">戒＝病【宋】，〔戒〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118015"><lem>戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">病</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>不能攝心不修<note n="1118016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智慧＝經義【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智慧＝經義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118016"><lem>智慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">經義</rdg></app>。二
<lb n="1118a24" ed="T"/><note n="1118017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝白【聖】</note><app n="1118017"><lem>自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">白</rdg></app>讀文字不<note n="1118018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">識＝諦【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">識＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118018"><lem>識</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">諦</rdg></app>句<note n="1118019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">逗＝讀【宋】</note><app n="1118019"><lem>逗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">讀</rdg></app>。以上著下以下著上。
<lb n="1118a25" ed="T"/>頭尾顛倒不能解了義之所歸。自以為是。三
<lb n="1118a26" ed="T"/>明者呵之不從其教反懷瞋恨。謂相嫉&CB00107;。<note n="1118020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">識義＝議識【聖】</note><app n="1118020"><lem>識
<lb n="1118a27" ed="T"/>義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">議識</rdg></app>者少。多不別理<note n="1118021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咸＝成【元】</note><app n="1118021"><lem>咸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">成</rdg></app><note n="1118022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118022"><lem>云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app>為是。是為三事。令
<lb n="1118a28" ed="T"/>法毀滅。</p>
<lb n="1118a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118a2901">佛告<app source="1118013" type="＊"><lem>諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘。復有四事。令法毀滅。何謂為
<pb n="1118b" ed="T" id="T12.0395.1118b"/>
<lb n="1118b01" ed="T"/>四。一將來比丘<note n="1118023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（已捨…業））十二字＝（（捨空閑處修道之業））八字【聖】</note><app word-count="12" n="1118023"><lem>已捨家<note n="1118024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔業〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔業〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118024"><lem>業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>在空閑處不修
<lb n="1118b02" ed="T"/>道業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">捨空閑處修道之業</rdg></app>。二&CB00540;遊人間憒&CB00436;之中行<note n="1118025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＋（比丘）【三】【聖】</note><note n="1118025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（比丘）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="1118025"><lem>來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】">來比丘</rdg></app>談言。求好
<lb n="1118b03" ed="T"/>袈裟五色之服。三高<note n="1118026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聽＝望【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽＝望【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118026"><lem>聽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">望</rdg></app>遠視以為綺<note n="1118027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">雅＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雅＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118027"><lem>雅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飾</rdg></app>。自
<lb n="1118b04" ed="T"/>以高德無能及者。以雜<note n="1118028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">碎＋（之）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118028"><lem>碎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">碎之</rdg></app>智<note n="1118029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔比〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118029"><lem>比</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>日月<note n="1118030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之明＝比丘【宋】，之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><note n="1118030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之明＝比丘【宋】，＝之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118030"><lem>之明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">比丘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">之比丘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1118b05" ed="T"/>畜已。四不攝三事。不護根門。行婦女間。宣文
<lb n="1118b06" ed="T"/>飾辭。多言合<note n="1118031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">偶＝禍【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118031"><lem>偶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">禍</rdg></app>。以動人心。使清變濁。身行
<lb n="1118b07" ed="T"/>荒亂。正法廢遲。是為四事。令法毀滅。</p>
<lb n="1118b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118b0801">佛告比丘。復有五事。令法毀滅。何謂為五。
<lb n="1118b09" ed="T"/><note n="1118032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118032"><lem>一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>或有比丘。本以法故出家修道。廢深經教
<lb n="1118b10" ed="T"/>十二因緣三十七品。方等深妙玄虛之慧。智
<lb n="1118b11" ed="T"/>度無極。善權方便。空無相願至化之<note n="1118033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">節＝第【聖】</note><app n="1118033"><lem>節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">第</rdg></app>。二
<lb n="1118b12" ed="T"/>反習雜句淺<note n="1118034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔末〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118034"><lem>末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>小<note n="1118035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（輩）【宮】</note><app n="1118035"><lem>經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">經輩</rdg></app>。世俗行故。<note n="1118036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＝三【三】</note><note n="1118036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118036"><lem>王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>者經典
<lb n="1118b13" ed="T"/>亂道之原。好講此業。易解世事。趣得人心令
<lb n="1118b14" ed="T"/>其歡<note n="1118037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喜＝悅【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝悅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118037"><lem>喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悅</rdg></app>。因致名聞<note n="1118038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三〕－【宋】【宮】，三＝四【元】【明】</note><app n="1118038"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">四</rdg></app>新聞法人。淺解之士
<lb n="1118b15" ed="T"/>意用妙快。深達之<note n="1118039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">士＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">士＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118039"><lem>士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>不用為<note n="1118040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佳＝法【聖】</note><app n="1118040"><lem>佳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">法</rdg></app>。<note n="1118041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔四〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔四〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118041"><lem>四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>天龍鬼
<lb n="1118b16" ed="T"/>神不以為喜。心懷悒慼口<note n="1118042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">發斯＝能發【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">發斯＝能發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118042"><lem>發斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">能發</rdg></app>言。大法欲滅
<lb n="1118b17" ed="T"/>故使其然。捨妙<note n="1118043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法化＝化法【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法化＝化法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118043"><lem>法化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化法</rdg></app>反宣雜句。諸天流淚速
<lb n="1118b18" ed="T"/>逝而去。五<note n="1118044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">由＋（說）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＋（說）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118044"><lem>由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由說</rdg></app>是正法稍稍見捨無精修者。是
<lb n="1118b19" ed="T"/>為五事。令法毀滅。</p>
<lb n="1118b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT12p1118b2001">佛告比丘。吾滅度後。有此邪事十<note n="1118045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝四【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五＝四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118045"><lem>五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">四</rdg></app>之亂令
<lb n="1118b21" ed="T"/>法毀滅。一何痛哉。若有比丘欲諦學道。棄捐
<lb n="1118b22" ed="T"/>綺飾不求名聞。質<note n="1118046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">朴＝科【三】</note><note n="1118046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">朴＝科【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118046"><lem>朴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">科</rdg></app>守真宣傳正經。佛之雅
<lb n="1118b23" ed="T"/>典深法之<note n="1118047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">化＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118047"><lem>化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辭</rdg></app>不用多言。案<note n="1118048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本說＝其本【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本說＝其本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118048"><lem>本說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其本</rdg></app>經不捨正
<lb n="1118b24" ed="T"/>句。希言屢中不失佛意。&CB00308;衣趣食。得美不甘
<lb n="1118b25" ed="T"/>得&CB00308;不<note n="1118049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡＝&CB01158;【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118049"><lem>惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&CB01158;</rdg></app>。衣食好醜隨施者意不以瞋喜。
<lb n="1118b26" ed="T"/><note n="1118050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">攝＝護【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攝＝護【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118050"><lem>攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">護</rdg></app>身口意守諸根門不違佛教。<note n="1118051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＝壽【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝壽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118051"><lem>念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">壽</rdg></app>命甚<note n="1118052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">矩＝短【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矩＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118052"><lem>矩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">短</rdg></app>
<lb n="1118b27" ed="T"/>恍<note n="1118053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惚＝忽【聖】</note><app n="1118053"><lem>惚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">忽</rdg></app><note n="1118054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118054"><lem>以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>過。如夢所見覺不知<note n="1118055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處＝虛【宋】</note><app n="1118055"><lem>處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">虛</rdg></app>。三塗之難
<lb n="1118b28" ed="T"/>不可稱計。勤修佛法猶救頭然。五戒十善六
<lb n="1118b29" ed="T"/>度無極。四等四恩智慧善權。咸可<note n="1118056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">精＝修【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精＝修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118056"><lem>精</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">修</rdg></app>行。<note n="1118057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">雖＋（復後生）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雖＋（復後生）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118057"><lem>雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雖復後生</rdg></app>
<pb n="1118c" ed="T" id="T12.0395.1118c"/>
<lb n="1118c01" ed="T"/>不值佛世出家為道學不唐捐。<note n="1118058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">平＝卒【宮】</note><app n="1118058"><lem>平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">卒</rdg></app>其本心愍
<lb n="1118c02" ed="T"/><note n="1118059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＝哀【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118059"><lem>念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">哀</rdg></app>一切十方蒙恩。佛說如是。諸比丘悲喜前
<lb n="1118c03" ed="T"/>自歸佛。作禮而去。</p>
<lb n="1118c04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan></div1>
